<I c="Tutorial" i="tutorial" m="tutorials.tutorial" n="tutorial_Beginner_Cheats" s="313989">
  <T n="name">0xACEB287A<!--String: "Cheats"--></T>
  <L n="slides">
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\Beginner\Beginner_Cheats_1.png">2f7d0004:00000000:2d427a09989489a6</T>
      <T n="text">0x33F059A8<!--String: "Bend the rules a little and try some <b><font color='#199C2C'>cheats</font></b>! Cheating is not a bad thing if it makes your experience more fun. \n\nTo toggle the <b><font color='#199C2C'>cheat console</font></b>, press <b><font color='#199C2C'>[Ctrl] + [Shift] + [C]</font></b> on your keyboard. Then, write a <b><font color='#199C2C'>cheat code</font></b> in the console and press <b><font color='#199C2C'>[Enter]</font></b> to activate it."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\Beginner\Beginner_Cheats_2.png">2f7d0004:00000000:2d427a09989489a5</T>
      <T n="text">0x2649C15E<!--String: "Who said you had to work hard to make <b><font color='#199C2C'>money</font></b>? Just use the following cheat codes in the console:\n \n<b><font color='#199C2C'>motherlode</font></b> gives the Household 50,000 Simoleons.\n\n<b><font color='#199C2C'>kaching</font></b> gives the Household 1,000 Simoleons.\n\n<b><font color='#199C2C'>FreeRealEstate on</font></b> can be activated in the World Map to make all houses cost 0 Simoleons."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\Beginner\Beginner_Cheats_3.png">2f7d0004:00000000:2d427a09989489a4</T>
      <T n="text">0x3023108D<!--String: "A great Build Mode cheat is <b><font color='#199C2C'>bb.moveObjects on</font></b>. This allows you to place items in locations that would otherwise be <b><font color='#199C2C'>invalid</font></b>! Be aware that some Objects might not work as intended when placed at an invalid location, but it works great for things like lush gardens and cluttered corners.\n\n<b><font color='#199C2C'>bb.ignoreGameplayUnlocksEntitlement</font></b> can be used to unlock otherwise locked Objects in the Build catalog, such as Career rewards."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\Beginner\Beginner_Cheats_4.png">2f7d0004:00000000:2d427a09989489a3</T>
      <T n="text">0xA0F6F930<!--String: "<b><font color='#199C2C'>testingcheats on</font></b> is a very special cheat code that unlocks more <b><font color='#199C2C'>advanced</font></b> cheats. \n\nFor example, after using this cheat code, you can use <b><font color='#199C2C'>Sims.fill_all_commodities</font></b> cheat code to fill the Needs of all the Sims in the Household. \n\nYou can also hold down the <b><font color='#199C2C'>[Shift]</font></b> key on the keyboard while <b><font color='#199C2C'>clicking</font></b> a Sim, select <b><font color='#199C2C'>Cheat Need…</font></b>, and then select <b><font color='#199C2C'>Make Happy</font></b> to max out all Needs, or disable Needs decay entirely by selecting <b><font color='#199C2C'>Disable Need Decay</font></b>."--></T>
    </U>
  </L>
